 prosperity for all.</p><p>3. Establish a second bill of rights to defend the dignity of all people and prioritize equality and equity for historically oppressed communities.</p><p><br></p><p>Send us an email (sunrisehunterdon@gmail.com) or sign up below to join the fight for our future.</p>","email":"sunrisehunterdon@gmail.com","website":null,"twitter":"https://twitter.com/hc_sunrise","facebook":"https://www.facebook.com/sunrisehunterdon/","instagram":"https://instagram.com/sunrisehunterdon","signup":"http://bit.ly/sunrisehunterdon","donations":null,"websiteText":null,"logo":null,"hero":null,"documents":[]}},"pageContext":{"id":"a370293b-adfb-506c-a53f-a867c66e7e98"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1219170061","3649515864"]}